  <prompt>Test the full secure project creation flow end-to-end: wizard with secure toggle → BU created → SPE container provisioned → Account created → project record has all references. Verify in Dataverse.</prompt>
  <role>You are a QA engineer writing end-to-end tests for the secure project creation flow.</role>
  <goal>Verified that the complete secure project creation flow works correctly, with all infrastructure provisioned and all references stored.</goal>
  <context>
    <background>The secure project creation flow is the entry point for the entire module. If this flow fails, nothing else works. This E2E test verifies the full chain: wizard toggle → API provisioning → Dataverse record verification.</background>
    <relevant-files>
      <file>tests/e2e/ (create test files)</file>
    </relevant-files>
  </context>
